  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/e6d7888ea5e71e09d4e51d1dbe289c0e.poster.avif?t=1726319976\" width=616 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/e6d7888ea5e71e09d4e51d1dbe289c0e.webm?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/e6d7888ea5e71e09d4e51d1dbe289c0e.mp4?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Expanding your island makes it possible to grow more plants. You are able to cook lots of meals with these plants and improve your income to buy new things for your farm. Be careful! As the island grows, the rent you pay will increase too. If you can’t pay the rent, say goodbye to the island!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/40ff129ebe92b913f66b369837709189.poster.avif?t=1726319976\" width=616 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/40ff129ebe92b913f66b369837709189.webm?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/40ff129ebe92b913f66b369837709189.mp4?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every day orders come to you by hungry people. If you can complete these orders, you can earn experiance point and gold. If you want to cook different meals, you should unlock all cards. Difficult meals more valuable! These orders will be significant for expand island and unlock new cards. You can unlock new cards to find new recipes. Also you can get some randomly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/9e486f13044af95c45027b68f12afefe.poster.avif?t=1726319976\" width=616 height=98 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/9e486f13044af95c45027b68f12afefe.webm?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292030/extras/9e486f13044af95c45027b68f12afefe.mp4?t=1726319976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>When island expand, things can get tough. You couldn't to water and havest all plants! For these issues you should use important tools.",
